oai_dc:dc.dc:title: St. John's Episcopal Church, Knoxville, TN, 1891
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: unknown
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: St. John's P.E. (Episcopal) Church, Cumberland & Walnut, Knoxville, TN. Taken just before it was torn down. July 14, 1891. Annie McGee and Calvin McClung were married in this church, the first wedding in this building.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Episcopal churches;
